# Border Options Test
# Tests BorderRadius, BorderColor, BorderWidth, and Padding
Output examples/svgs/templates/border-test.svg

Set Width 600
Set Height 300
Set FontSize 16
Set Theme verminal
Set Title "Border Test"
Set BorderRadius 20
Set BorderWidth 3
Set BorderColor #ff3b30
Set Padding 32

Type "echo 'Testing border options'"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Type "# BorderRadius: 20, BorderWidth: 3"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Type "# BorderColor: #ff3b30, Padding: 32"
Sleep 1s
